

Todays Soft Skill Tip:

Day 32 – Listening to Learn: Turning Every Chat into Growth

We often listen to reply - but growth begins when you listen to understand.

When you focus fully on another person’s words, tone, and pauses, you pick up lessons that no textbook can teach.

Real learners listen twice before speaking once.

Task:

In your next conversation, set one rule: no interrupting.
At the end, summarize what you understood in one line.

You’ll be amazed how much sharper your comprehension becomes.
